<h3><span id="Male_communities_.28cloistered_monks.29"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Male_communities_(cloistered_monks)">Male communities (cloistered monks)</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hieronymites&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Male communities (cloistered monks)"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Monastery_of_Santa_Mar%C3%ADa_del_Parral" title="Monastery of Santa María del Parral">Monastery of Saint Mary of Parral</a> (<a href="/wiki/Segovia" title="Segovia">Segovia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Spain" title="Spain">Spain</a>) – Founded in 1447</li></ul>
